    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends to stack trash, climb up, and avoid danger in this fun and hectic multiplayer party game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as one of five different toys and climb as high as you can through the garbage chute! Stack a variety of trash and create your own road to freedom. But be careful! For many hazards await you in your quest for survival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't touch the buzzsaw! It rips everything apart - trash, players and maybe even friendships... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be wary of the crusher: it may not look as dangerous as the buzzsaw, but it packs a solid punch when it comes to flattening trash... and you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this test of teamwork, creativity and stamina... Will you become the MVP, or the trash teammate?</p>",
